text: FCCP may be: * Fellow of the College of Chest Physicians, a Fellow of the American College of Chest Physicians * Fellow of the American College of Clinical Pharmacy, a Fellow of the American College of Clinical Pharmacy * Fellow of the Ceylon College of Physicians, a Fellow of the Ceylon College of Physicians, Sri Lanka * Carbonyl cyanide-p-trifluoromethoxyphenylhydrazone, a hydrazone compound used in biochemistry
title: FCCP
